  "prompt": "How do i get NBA 2K17 Redeem Code?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, obtaining a redeem code for NBA 2K17 may be challenging because the game is somewhat old and support for it may have dwindled. However, here are a few suggestions on how you might be able to get one:\n\n1. **Retail Purchase**: If you purchase a physical copy of NBA 2K17 from a retailer, it may come with a redeem code inside.\n\n2. **Second-Hand Marketplaces**: Websites like eBay or Craigslist could have listings for NBA 2K17 that include redeem codes. Make sure to verify the legitimacy of the seller and the code.\n\n3. **Online Storefronts**: Sometimes digital stores like Amazon, GameStop, or Best Buy might still have digital codes for older games. \n\n4. **Promotions and Giveaways**: Follow social media channels and forums that relate to NBA 2K or gaming in general, sometimes users or companies might hold giveaways or promotions.\n\n5. **Contacting Support**: Although unlikely, you could try contacting the game's support team to see if they can assist you in any way.\n\nPlease be cautious when seeking codes from less reputable sources as scams can be prevalent. It's always safest to use trusted platforms and shops.",
